<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 12:12:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的品牌：没有责任，没有责任，没有悔恨</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-on-brand-no-responsibility-no-accountability-no-remorse/0000018b-288d-d450-a3af-699d263a0000</link><description>周四，本杰明·内塔尼亚胡组建了“临时战时内阁”，将他的零责任、始终分担责任的态度提升到了一个新的水平。在任何其他情况下，这都是正确的做法——对他来说，这只是确保加沙战争失败的责任归咎于其他人的另一种方式</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 11:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-on-brand-no-responsibility-no-accountability-no-remorse/0000018b-288d-d450-a3af-699d263a0000</guid></item><item><title>人质是以色列的致命弱点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hostages-are-israels-achilles-heel/0000018b-2622-d3fc-a3bf-bfef934e0000</link><description>被哈马斯在加沙绑架的以色列人（其中包括妇女、儿童、婴儿和老人）的视频和图像令人痛苦，触动了以色列政体最柔软、最脆弱的弱点</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 10:18:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hostages-are-israels-achilles-heel/0000018b-2622-d3fc-a3bf-bfef934e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列新的哈马斯-加沙概念注定会失败，就像上一个概念一样</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-concept-of-hamas-and-gaza-is-doomed-to-fail-just-like-the-last-one/0000018b-27bb-d1bc-a58b-6fbf9edf0000</link><description>以色列对待哈马斯的态度是错误的，将其视为一个政治组织，可以通过经济激励来影响其取得成果。像对待伊斯兰国一样对哈马斯发动战争是一个谬论，它掩盖了加沙地带冲突后控制问题</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 10:17:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-concept-of-hamas-and-gaza-is-doomed-to-fail-just-like-the-last-one/0000018b-27bb-d1bc-a58b-6fbf9edf0000</guid></item><item><title>在美国和欧洲的支持下，以色列正在摧毁加沙。它必须考虑后天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/with-u-s-and-european-support-israel-is-crushing-gaza-it-must-think-about-the-day-after/0000018b-2802-dff1-a5eb-feff0c720000</link><description>哈马斯的恐怖袭击和以色列受害者的数量令人难以想象。与此同时，加沙人面临的只有地狱和毁灭。一旦复仇的欲望稍稍消退，我们必须要问：加沙将会发生什么？</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 09:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/with-u-s-and-european-support-israel-is-crushing-gaza-it-must-think-about-the-day-after/0000018b-2802-dff1-a5eb-feff0c720000</guid></item><item><title>加沙地带的起源及其周围的以色列社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-origins-of-the-gaza-strip-and-the-israeli-communities-nestled-by-it/0000018b-23fe-d680-af9b-23fe94490000</link><description>加沙汹涌的仇恨之海正是这些以色列社区本应“笼罩”的</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 09:43:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-origins-of-the-gaza-strip-and-the-israeli-communities-nestled-by-it/0000018b-23fe-d680-af9b-23fe94490000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军监测以色列-加沙边境的气球在哈马斯袭击前几周破裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/idf-balloons-monitoring-israel-gaza-border-broke-down-weeks-before-hamas-attack/0000018b-2831-d1bc-a58b-69b7dd400000</link><description>以色列军队上周未能修复边境监控技术；目前正在研究哈马斯破坏气球的可能性</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 09:32:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/idf-balloons-monitoring-israel-gaza-border-broke-down-weeks-before-hamas-attack/0000018b-2831-d1bc-a58b-69b7dd400000</guid></item><item><title>研究揭示了中东史前暴力的范围</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-13/ty-article/study-reveals-the-scope-of-prehistoric-violence-in-the-middle-east/0000018b-2416-d3fc-a3bf-bfffeddc0000</link><description>对 14,000 至 2,400 年前的 3,500 具骨骼的分析发现了暴力历史中的细微差别。有时可以包容</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 06:16:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-13/ty-article/study-reveals-the-scope-of-prehistoric-violence-in-the-middle-east/0000018b-2416-d3fc-a3bf-bfffeddc0000</guid></item><item><title>这就是乌克兰与以色列站在一起的原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/this-is-why-ukraine-stands-with-israel/0000018b-2629-d680-af9b-26ef410a0000</link><description>针对以色列的可怕恐怖袭击引起了乌克兰人的共鸣。火箭、酷刑和谋杀、绑架儿童——我们太了解这个剧本了。但我们的悲剧的相似之处并非偶然</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 06:02:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/this-is-why-ukraine-stands-with-israel/0000018b-2629-d680-af9b-26ef410a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙和黎巴嫩之间行走，等待真主党的下一步行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/dogged-by-nightmares-israel-walks-a-thin-line-between-gaza-and-lebanon/0000018b-255b-d680-af9b-27dfe0390000</link><description>以色列军队必须决定是应该集中在一条战线还是两条战线上 ■ 导致最终失败的误解和情报错误 ■ 现在指责那些对恐怖事件负责的人还为时过早 ■ 违反与人民的契约</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 04:32:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/dogged-by-nightmares-israel-walks-a-thin-line-between-gaza-and-lebanon/0000018b-255b-d680-af9b-27dfe0390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列：一个饱受创伤、失去政府的国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-a-country-in-trauma-bereft-of-government/0000018b-2579-d3fc-a3bf-bffd6baa0000</link><description>以色列人现在有一种倒置的无政府状态，这激发了整个国家的希望 ■ 对于内塔尼亚胡来说，分裂不是一个错误，而是一个特征</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 03:53:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-a-country-in-trauma-bereft-of-government/0000018b-2579-d3fc-a3bf-bffd6b