往我们灵魂中最黑暗的地方之外对任何人来说都无处可去的道路”</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 20:59:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-vows-to-crush-hamas-as-u-s-u-k-pledge-support-for-israel/0000018b-2579-d680-af9b-27ff55080000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，特朗普询问主要亲以色列盟友是否可以在哈马斯袭击后呼吁“立即弹劾”内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/trump-wants-netanyahu-impeached-over-hamas-attacks-rolling-stone-reports/0000018b-2592-d680-af9b-27de3c360000</link><description>该报告发布前几个小时，特朗普公开批评内塔尼亚胡和以色列情报机构允许哈马斯袭击发生，并指出如果 2020 年选举没有“操纵”，这种袭击永远不会发生</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 20:56:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-12/ty-article/trump-wants-netanyahu-impeached-over-hamas-attacks-rolling-stone-reports/0000018b-2592-d680-af9b-27de3c360000</guid></item><item><title>“他们向我开枪，爸爸，”我儿子说。我必须尽力拯救他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/theyre-shooting-at-me-dad-my-son-said-i-had-to-try-to-save-him/0000018b-2529-d680-af9b-27ef90b60000</link><description>我问我的儿子，他当时正在被哈马斯袭击的超新星狂欢节上，他的确切位置在哪里，我根本不明白他在说什么，我说：“我来了，我来了。”我听到背景中有枪声，电话就被挂断了</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 20:31:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/theyre-shooting-at-me-dad-my-son-said-i-had-to-try-to-save-him/0000018b-2529-d680-af9b-27ef90b60000</guid></item></channel></rss>